    "description": "Woodland Greens is a relaxing and casual mini-golf experience, perfect for short and enjoyable gameplay sessions. Step into a peaceful world inspired by the beauty of the British countryside, where each playthrough offers something new and exciting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224260/extras/255f8f9aa6b00e50b70fdbaa092624e2.poster.avif?t=1754105082\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224260/extras/255f8f9aa6b00e50b70fdbaa092624e2.webm?t=1754105082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224260/extras/255f8f9aa6b00e50b70fdbaa092624e2.mp4?t=1754105082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every time you play, a brand-new course is procedurally generated, ensuring no two games are alike. Tackle slopes, navigate tricky obstacles like windmills and water ditches, and test your precision on challenging terrain. Beyond the traditional mini-golf experience, Woodland Greens encourages exploration with collectible stars scattered throughout the courses, adding an extra layer of fun and discovery.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224260/extras/7bd47f522ab2667fd66f000ae7e05eca.poster.avif?t=1754105082\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224260/extras/7bd47f522ab2667fd66f000ae7e05eca.webm?t=1754105082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224260/extras/7bd47f522ab2667fd66f000ae7e05eca.mp4?t=1754105082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With an almost limitless variety of randomly generated courses, Woodland Greens guarantees hours of laid-back enjoyment, whether you're aiming for a relaxing break or mastering the art of the perfect putt.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br>Woodland Greens offers a stress-free experience as all gameplay features are fully unlocked from the very beginning. There are no difficult or frustrating challenges required to unlock additional features.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stylized hand-painted 3D artwork<br></li><li>Procedurally generated courses<br></li><li>5 course sizes from 'Very Small' to 'Very Large'<br></li><li>Simple and accessible controls<br></li><li>Relaxing gameplay<br></li><li>Almost 40 Steam achievements to attain</li></ul>",
